**No, you don't need `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` on .NET 10.** That property is only for .NET 9 and earlier.

On .NET 10, use the native MTP mode by adding a `test` section to your `global.json`:

```json
{
  "sdk": {
    "version": "10.0.100"
  },
  "test": {
    "runner": "Microsoft.Testing.Platform"
  }
}
```

